{"tid":1254174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(撤出中国) 法國家樂福集團售出當地80％投資事業  由中国蘇寧買下","createTime":"2019-06-24T03:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T03:41:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ce33c416a98d870aa5dd72649c93df68ab85b8","tid":1254174,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"法商家樂福（Carrefour）今（23）日表示，已將其於中國市場的80%事業出售給中國蘇寧易購網。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，歐洲規模最大的零售商法國家樂福集團今（23）日對外發出聲明表示，已將該集團80%的中國事售予中國蘇寧易購網。<br />\n<br />\n據聲明內容，交易合約內中國家樂福扣除債務後價值約14億歐元，待中國監管機關同意後，預計於2019年底前結束營業。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，家樂福在中國擁有210座大賣場、24家便利商店，資料顯示，中國家樂福2018年網路購物營收達36億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2831356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2831356&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=7829cb54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2831356&h=fea239c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2831356</a>"},{"pid":"cd3ca4fb7eb9aa088ab2f2db5d830b35c294f3ba","tid":1254174,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:41:19.000Z","msg":"以前香港都有家樂福"}]}